snippet.title: Amber Academy Webinar - Cry: an in depth analysis of the prologue of "The Last of Us" by Dave Pimm
snippet.description:
Dave Pimm will be joining us for a webinar entitled Cry, shining a new light on one of the most popular games from the last years, "The Last of Us".
Dave is a Lecturer at the University of Suffolk, having a twelve years hands-on experience (on and off) with the games industry, working on AAA and indie titles as an artist, designer, writer and creative director. He also studies the psychology behind games and the emotions that trigger us.
